{"tid":1698973,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(代post) 唔好再叫啲狗做阿sir！被捕唔洗跪，唔係阻差辦公","createTime":"2019-11-08T01:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:02.000Z","uid":318817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6114ffecd0ab991ec8eb7683c07021c93b3832d","tid":1698973,"uid":318817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱同咗同班狗屌咗廿年嘅朋友傾計，佢好想我幫手宣傳一個message<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好再叫班狗做阿sir！</span></span><br />\n我地要攞走佢地嘅光環，因為呢個稱呼代表社會上有地位嘅人，係個尊稱，而佢地唔配呢個稱呼！<br />\n即係語氣寸佢地都好，其實係比梗個機會佢地自我感覺良好，例如佢地會話 阿sir做野唔洗你教<br />\n當佢地叫梗我地做曱甴，將我地去人性化，點解我地要比個尊稱佢地？？<br />\n<br />\n另外，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">被捕唔洗跪，唔洗雙手擺頭，唔洗搭膊頭上車</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>絕對唔係阻差辦公！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"515a597efedd171bae672102d101cf56e27564f8","tid":1698973,"uid":318817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<br />\nReference在此: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191101/II4CECNPMQNQMXIZTHFSFYOEVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191101%2FII4CECNPMQNQMXIZTHFSFYOEVQ%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=0387216a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191101%2FII4CECNPMQNQMXIZTHFSFYOEVQ%2F&h=4144d166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191101/II4CECNPMQNQMXIZTHFSFYOEVQ/</a>"},{"pid":"6547285417c67e8155ff6681db773b4475b6e537","tid":1698973,"uid":314510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n不過我都推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}